name: Runika
description:
I have studied the goddess within the female personality based on the archetypal approach of the famous psychologist Jung. Aphrodite is a female archetype whose appearance reflects her inner charm and reveals the characteristics of feminine energy. Love and beauty are indescribable. She loves the harmony of colors and pristine and poetic nature, creativity, elegance, liberation in life and dynamism are crystallized in it. My illustrations try to show these special characteristics in relation to women for better understanding.
Size: 50 .70 cm - resolution 300 dpi
